4. POLITICALLY EXPOSED PERSON (PEP) DECLARATION

   By accessing or using the Software, you hereby voluntarily declare, represent,
   warrant, and covenant that:

   (a) PEP Status: You are NOT, and have not been within the past twelve (12)
       months, a Politically Exposed Person ("PEP") as defined by the Financial
       Action Task Force (FATF), including but not limited to:

       (i) Any individual who is or has been entrusted with a prominent public
           function in any country, including heads of state or government,
           senior politicians, senior government officials, judicial or military
           officials, senior executives of state-owned corporations, or important
           political party officials;

       (ii) Any individual who holds or has held a prominent function within an
            international organization, including members of senior management or
            individuals who have been entrusted with equivalent functions;

       (iii) Any domestic PEP as defined under applicable local law or
             regulation;

   (b) Family Members and Close Associates: You are NOT an immediate family
       member (including spouse, domestic partner, parent, sibling, child, or
       spouse's parent or sibling) or known close associate (including any
       individual known to have joint beneficial ownership of legal entities or
       business relationships, or any other close business relations) of any PEP
       as defined above;

   (c) Ongoing Obligation: You agree to immediately cease using the Software
       and notify the Providers if you become a PEP or an immediate family
       member or known close associate of a PEP at any time;

   (d) Accuracy of Representation: You acknowledge that this representation is
       material and that the Providers are relying upon the accuracy of this
       representation in permitting you to access and use the Software.

   ANY BREACH OF THIS REPRESENTATION AND WARRANTY SHALL CONSTITUTE A MATERIAL
   BREACH OF THIS LICENSE AND SHALL RESULT IN IMMEDIATE TERMINATION OF YOUR
   RIGHT TO ACCESS AND USE THE SOFTWARE.

5. RESTRICTED JURISDICTIONS

   This software may NOT be accessed, downloaded, installed, or used by any
