8. NON-CUSTODIAL SOFTWARE

   This is non-custodial, open-source research software. No Provider has access
   to, custody of, or control over your private keys, seed phrases, or funds.
   No Provider operates any servers that hold or transmit your assets, has the
   ability to recover lost keys or reverse transactions, or intermediates,
   facilitates, or processes any transactions on your behalf.

   You alone are responsible for securing your private keys and seed phrases.
   If you lose access to them, your funds are permanently unrecoverable.

9. PPOI SPENDING REQUIREMENT

   All funds must be verified through the Private Proof of Innocence (PPOI)
   system provided by the official PPOI network at https://ppoi.fdi.network/
   before they can be spent. You may not use this software to interact with
   balances unless they have a valid PPOI status verified through the official
   PPOI aggregator.

10. NETWORK CONNECTIONS DISCLOSURE

    This software makes direct network connections to external services including
    RPC nodes, Subsquid indexers, PPOI aggregator nodes, IPFS gateways (for
    downloading zero-knowledge proof artifacts), and Blockscout APIs (for public
    transaction history). Your IP address may be visible to these services. No
    Provider is responsible for any privacy breaches resulting from these network
    connections.

